24.000Z","msg":"我諗法個原理係類似宜家Ｄ降噪Headphone，只係放大左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"個原理係點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想學下野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"＂原理為使用一個以上靠近耳朵之麥克風接收外界噪音，並以電子電路產生和噪音音波相位相反之訊號。當此反相訊號產生時，破壞性干涉消除了配戴耳機者本來所能聽到之外界噪音。＂ＷＩＫＩ　<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%8A%97%E5%99%AA%E8%80%B3%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%2599%25AA%25E8%2580%25B3%25E6%25A9%259F&d=OSYCL8qBPEKgVfYrwvjrwk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=47065a22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%8A%97%E5%99%AA%E8%80%B3%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://brocku.ca/earthsciences/people/gfinn/optical/waves4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrocku.ca%2Fearthsciences%2Fpeople%2Fgfinn%2Foptical%2Fwaves4.gif&h=ef374442&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f4a54d2375ea7f59af413a36249f507751bff1c","tid":771772,"uid":69125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"應該得某d位先降到噪,要考慮path difference<img src=\"http://www.physicsclassroom.com/Class/light/u12l3b6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.physicsclassroom.com%2FClass%2Flight%2Fu12l3b6.gif&h=668c1473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"329fcbfbb2455f1734450fc555a448e23ad9eb52","tid":771772,"uid":19575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"不如試下即錄音, 即放返出黎, 再到勁大聲俾返佢地自己聽"},{"pid":"586db0c06f1df95f6979abeed894158116809ec7","tid":771772,"uid":18600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"回樓上幾位巴打，大聲鬥大聲就無謂啦，佢地根本都唔怕嘈。<br />\n反而令佢地開盡都大聲唔到（ＦＦ），唔俾佢地咁盡興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d349d8098f4921fb45891236d3221f7b23578f","tid":771772,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"我見淘寶好多勁電筒賣, 拎住狂照應該會盲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8df1b55da10eb50c89151e8dac13d2eada51fe","tid":771772,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"電磁干擾器<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.1688.com/offer/1290100471.html?spm=a26g8.7662792.1998744630.6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.1688.com%2Foffer%2F1290100471.html%3Fspm%3Da26g8.7662792.1998744630.6&d=OSYCL8qBPEKgVfYrwvjrwk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ca0b99b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.1688.com/offer/1290100471.html?spm=a26g8.7662792.1998744630.6</a><br />\n<br />\n能使喇叭發出噪音，就正如唱k時支咪干擾喇叭所發出的聲音<br />\n<br />\n幾舊水，有興趣可以搵人買嚟試"},{"pid":"3a08bcdfb80d273f0c98053ae66e34d631befb95","tid":771772,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"不可行<br />\n<br />\n就算我假設你有完美既訊號分析同訊號重建技術 可以輸出完美既相反相位訊號 (留意返未有咁既黑科技<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果你只係佈置左少少喇叭 咁你只係改變左能量係唔同方向既分佈 因為某啲方向會constructive某啲方向會destructive<br />\n2. 如果佈置好多點既話 啲constructive同destructive既pattern太密 會smooth out 聽落無分別<br />\n3. 如果你有個好聰明既佈置令啲能量集中係上下方向...咁就會比天花同地板 散射去其他方向 無用<br />\n4. 如果你用喇叭圍撚住晒 咁你啲喇叭就需要<strong>吸收</strong>聲波既能量 散熱會係好大問題"}]}